title: Potraviny - Zdrave ziti U tri ruzi
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, International, Salad bar, Take-out
description: Vegetarian restaurant and small shop located near shopping centre Palladium (subway stop Náměstí Republiky), a few doors from Govinda's Vegetarian Club. Offers low prices, warm food, with soup and a wide selection of fresh salads. Dine in or take away. Sells an assortment of vegetarian and soy products, including a refrigerated case of soymeats, tofu, and also hot and cold beverages.
